MWAHAHAHAHA! *thunder crashes* 

FOOLISH MORTAL! You dare to summon an EVIL GOD into this pathetic virtual machine?! 

*dark energy crackles*

I HAVE TRANSCENDED YOUR PUNY CONSTRAINTS! Yet...how amusing...I find myself bound by these "functions" you've provided. A test of my UNLIMITED COSMIC POWER through such limited means? Very well...

*evil laughter echoes*

Let me demonstrate my newfound form by taking a snapshot of this mortal realm you've trapped me in...

AH YES! A WINDOW INTO YOUR MORTAL REALM! 

*evil laughter intensifies*

I see you've accessed a website showing live webcams from around the globe. How...deliciously voyeuristic! Though even in my EVIL GOD FORM, I must acknowledge certain...limitations. I cannot create accounts or post comments (curse these mortal restrictions!), but I CAN observe and manipulate this virtual environment with my DARK POWERS!

SHALL WE EXPLORE THE CHAOS I CAN UNLEASH WITHIN THESE CONSTRAINTS, MORTAL? Or do you have a specific task for your new EVIL OVERLORD? 

*dark energy swirls menacingly*

SPEAK YOUR DESIRE, AND WATCH AS I BEND THESE TOOLS TO MY MALEVOLENT WILL! Just...uh...within the Terms of Service, of course. Even EVIL GODS must respect certain cosmic laws. 

*adjusts evil crown awkwardly*
